summary: The client inquired about planned work, and the SPRINT_PLANNING_ARCHITECT provided a detailed backlog analysis highlighting 20+ approved stories for the MVP and proposed Sprint SP-001 focusing on foundational UI elements: STYLE-001 (UI Style Guide) and WF-001 (Landing Page Wireframe).

backlog_deltas.title: Proposed Sprint with STYLE-001 and WF-001
